{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-black-copy","title":"REGULAR CROPPED TEE - BLACK","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Relaxed Waist. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for effortless everyday wear. Crafted with a clean, minimal aesthetic, it features a regular fit with a relaxed waistline that offers comfort without compromising structure. The cropped length adds a modern edge, making it easy to style across casual and elevated looks. Made from combed and bio-washed cotton, this tee delivers a soft hand feel, breathability, and long-lasting durability. A versatile essential built for comfort, balance, and timeless appeal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to avoid shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Regular-fit cropped design with a relaxed waist for easy movement and comfort. Gender-neutral silhouette suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton ensures all-day wearability. Bio-washed finish for enhanced durability a\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47448325947546,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47448325980314,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47448326013082,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47448326045850,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\